	"system": {
		"description": "<p><em>Passive: You gain resistance to cold damage, and ignore movement penalties from ice and snow.</em></p><p><em><strong>Legend Dice Feature</strong></em><strong> — Winter Requital:</strong> When a creature ends its turn within 5 feet of you, you can expend a Legend Die as a reaction to force it to make a Constitution saving throw (Maneuver DC). On a failure, its speed is halved until the end of its next turn and it takes cold damage equal to the result.</p>",
